<span id="dcbreak"></span>
 '''break:'''
     The break statement makes you break out of any
     loop you're currently in.

 '''Example:'''

 <nowiki>

 dilbegin foo();
   code
   {
     while (self.inside) {
       if (self.position &lt POSITION_SLEEPING)
         break;
       exec("say I own something", self);
       pause;
     }
   }
   dilend</nowiki>

